{"tid":641933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朝媒發金正恩探車禍傷者相　討好北京","createTime":"2018-04-25T11:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T14:07:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"701889a8320265851b72c40f7fe8cb64880bd8f4","tid":641933,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T11:18:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180425/20372137?_ga=2.11791156.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180425%2F20372137%3F_ga%3D2.11791156.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=qoaLjeZX213bv%2BDWR6IlbQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=f3df82b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180425%2F20372137%3F_ga%3D2.11791156.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=a2ee7a3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180425/20372137?_ga=2.11791156.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n8年04月25日 <br />\n<br />\n朝媒發金正恩探車禍傷者相　討好北京<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180425/large/25cf11p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180425%2Flarge%2F25cf11p.jpg&h=ab057c38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n北韓前晚發生重大死亡車禍，造成至少32名中國公民和4名北韓人喪生；北韓官方媒體昨報道，領導人金正恩對這件悲劇表示「沉痛哀傷」，並發佈金正恩到醫院探望傷者的照片（圖）。外媒指，北韓媒體罕見地報道這次略為負面的消息，以顯示北韓與中國的關係更為緊密。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民要求公開起因<br />\n<br />\n法新社報道稱，北韓政府一向嚴格管控對外消息，官方通訊社罕見地報道了這則負面新聞。路透社則報道，事件顯示中國是北韓經濟與外交上最重要的支持者。<br />\n<br />\n據北韓中央通信社報道，金正恩前日上午會見中國駐北韓大使，稍後到醫院探望車禍倖存者。報道稱，金正恩接到車禍消息後，對事故感到沉痛哀傷，想到那些失去親人的家庭時，他就哀傷不已。金正恩又說，北韓人民「對這件悲劇事故感同身受」，他將以「最大誠意」來處理善後，緩解家屬悲痛。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部昨表示，金正恩在23日晚專程到醫院看望兩名受重傷的中國公民，表示朝方會盡全力救治，並同中方一道做好事故處置和善後工作。中方對此表示感謝。內地網民認為金正恩此舉意在討好北京，「因有所圖」，另有網民則要求公佈事故原因。<br />\n<br />\n中央社  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n遼寧號東海晒馬威嚇日本<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n出席上合外長會議　印度拒撐一帶一路"},{"pid":"7517536791c0be79dc2104d1deb62c5097f3a3e7","tid":641933,"uid":32325,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T11:21:12.000Z","msg":"個feel似做緊人體實驗"},{"pid":"34f0c02458eb84f260365762ad53b5726b3814f3","tid":641933,"uid":12404,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T11:22:54.000Z","msg":"金仔探病做咩着醫生袍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee6916b7464567b8ff029f5ab6119b2dae63d2a","tid":641933,"uid":122740,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"34f0c02458eb84f260365762ad53b5726b3814f3","tid":641933,"uid":12404,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T11:22:54.000Z","msg":"金仔探病做咩着醫生袍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T11:24:33.000Z","msg":"因為佢係神醫 能醫百病<br />\n摸摸你就知咩病"},{"pid":"2cc166efc2f3be4481f3f871657e8bb67b08946c","tid":641933,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T11:44:59.000Z","msg":"2腳羊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"312b25ddc3497d3743fd4affbf95df81c7464674","tid":641933,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T11:48:16.000Z","msg":"真係睇唔透金仔呢啲係咩棋路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf252acae4746ee7f3944b84c7b02ef690858c8","tid":641933,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T11:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁叫討好北京<br />\n不如話驚比人發現單野係佢策劃"},{"pid":"88c1e752167ab022627a6c30577929cc3540c084","tid":641933,"uid":42636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T11:52:08.000Z","msg":"問緊個傷者影完相<br />\n想犬決定高射炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97045e5877e6a66025e8b1d7a337036fd7043cef","tid":641933,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T11:55:49.000Z","msg":"見到金生都唔喊唔感恩 高射炮決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504527e3b5638f4a80a5d1e48092208509c0d41f","tid":641933,"uid":42636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97045e5877e6a66025e8b1d7a337036fd7043cef","tid":641933,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T11:55:49.000Z","msg":"見到金生都唔喊唔感恩 高射炮決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T12:07:20.000Z","msg":"重要訓響到<br />\n冇感動位<br />\n下世小心d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d1679c9f218e620cf523eab3e4fc59513c3849","tid":641933,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T12:10:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>法新社報道稱，北韓政府一向嚴格管控對外消息，官方通訊社罕見地報道了這則負面新聞。</blockquote><br />\n負面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死既係支那人又唔係北泡, 無普天同慶算畀面喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9655d04fe89a2a08860c89e6e55e3579b532a109","tid":641933,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:36:27.000Z","msg":"要不是偉大金主席親自慰問下令全力搶救傷者，支那五毛早就全車死清光了。"},{"pid":"ee557b7cc2ba5d11798fcc062a78a7c9d16b12dd","tid":641933,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T14:07:28.000Z","msg":"朝媒發金正恩探車禍傷者相 中國或成最大贏家"}]}